    <p class="gem-c-title__context">
      Guidance
    </p>
  <h1 class="gem-c-title__text gem-c-title__text--long">
    Carry out international road haulage after Brexit
  </h1>
</div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
    
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph ">
    What UK goods vehicle operators need to do to carry out international road haulage if there's a no-deal Brexit.
  </p>

  </div>
</div>

<div class="govuk-grid-row">
  <div class="metadata-logo-wrapper">
